---
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 md:py-32'>

  <!-- Subtle grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(26,60,74,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(26,60,74,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 48px 48px;'>
  </div>

  <!-- Giant Titan One watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -left-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive; font-size: clamp(12rem, 25vw, 20rem); color: rgba(249,115,22,0.04); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'>
    €€€
  </div>

  <!-- Orange corner accent right -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-40 bg-orange-500 rounded-l-full'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <!-- Top hairline -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-petrol-100 to-transparent'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>
  <!-- Bottom hairline -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-petrol-100 to-transparent'
    aria-hidden='true'>
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8'>

    <!-- ── Section header ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class='mb-16 md:mb-20 max-w-3xl'>
      <div data-animate class='flex items-center gap-3 mb-8'>
        <span class='block h-px w-10 bg-orange-500' aria-hidden='true'></span>
        <span class='text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-orange-500'>
          Lo que me comprometo a hacer
        </span>
      </div>

      <h2
        data-animate
        style='font-family: "Titan One", cursive;'
        class='leading-[0.92] tracking-tight mb-6'>
        <span class='block text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3rem)] text-petrol-700'>
          Tienes que ganar
        </span>
        <span class='block text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] text-petrol-900'>
          más de lo que me pagas<span class='text-orange-400'>.</span>
        </span>
      </h2>

      <div data-animate class='flex items-center'>
        <div class='h-[3px] w-16 bg-orange-500 rounded-full'></div>
        <div class='h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/40 to-transparent'></div>
      </div>

      <p data-animate class='mt-6 text-base md:text-lg text-petrol-700 leading-relaxed text-pretty max-w-[52ch]'>
        Si me contratas, lo primero que hacemos juntos es calcular
        <strong class='font-semibold text-petrol-900'>cuánto dinero tiene que entrar por los clientes que te llegan desde Google</strong>.
        Si lo que me pagas no trae más de lo que cuesta, no tiene ningún sentido seguir.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
